title: S7E18 – "Into the Black" – Scary Stories Told in the Dark
description:
In this episode of Scary Stories Told in the Dark, we bring you four spine-chilling tales from author M.M. Kelley, performed by host and narrator Otis Jiry, about ominous encounters, ancient entities, aquatic atrocities, and inhuman horrors.
